{"id":373801,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/53/20/532070.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"～技术宅真可怕～","groupHref":"/group/a","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/00/11.jpg","message":"用电脑浏览器打开t.me链接(例如<a href=\"https://t.me/NC_Raws_Channel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">https://t.me/NC_Raws_Channel</a>)会显示2个按钮：<br><img width=\"200\" height=\"278\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/10/12/9dRWj1hgs8Y2cxe.png\" border=\"0\" alt class=\"code\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"><br>一个\"View in Telegram\"打开的是tg://resolve?domain=NC_Raws_Channel(应该是Telegram桌面应用使用的URL scheme)；另一个\"Preview channel\"打开的是<a href=\"https://t.me/s/NC_Raws_Channel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">https://t.me/s/NC_Raws_Channel</a>(多了一个/s），但是打开会重定向到当前页面所以根本无法preview<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">。<br><br>但是奇怪的是，如果用手机浏览器打开的话，下面的按钮就会变成\"Open in Web\"，链接是<a href=\"https://web.telegram.org/z/#?tgaddr=tg%3Aresolve%3Fdomain%3DNC_Raws_Channel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">https://web.telegram.org/z/#?tgaddr=tg%3Aresolve%3Fdomain%3DNC_Raws_Channel</a>而且确确实实是用Telegram Web Z打开的<br><img width=\"200\" height=\"420\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/10/12/dYtLlZCw61UxEmM.png\" border=\"0\" alt class=\"code\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"><br><br>那么问题来了，如何让电脑打开t.me链接才能和手机一样可以用Telegram Web打开呢<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>试过用浏览器的开发者工具来模拟手机，但是并没有什么变化<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/77.gif\" smileid=\"116\" alt=\"(bgm100)\"> ","time":"2022-10-12 17:40","title":"如何用Telegram Web打开t.me链接","userId":"posthumz","userName":"posthumz","userSign":""}